        "cooked": "<p>You are correct about the latest Briar release… I am not sure where I got the 7 years from, obviously a bad link from another site. And I apologize for posting my compile code errors, Signal is not the place for that… my bad. I do still have concerns over the source code, with the virus warning on a jpg file. I suppose I can just grab the apk file and try it out. I, myself, am not a biker and have no need for the program… Just doing some research for a friend in Scotland. <img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/images/emoji/apple/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>",
